OL,3,CTwo men and three teenagers charged
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged rape of girl
OL,6,FIonut Dobre, 33, of Cleanthus Road,
OL,7,FWoolwich, was charged with rape on
OL,8,FFriday, alongside two 16-year-olds and
OL,9,Fa 15-year-old, who cannot be named for
OL,10,Flegal reasons - all from Gravesend.
OL,12,FBenone Inofte, 46, of Salisbury Road,
OL,13,FGravesend, was also charged on Friday
OL,14,Fwith aiding and abetting a rape.
OL,16,FThey appeared at Medway Magistrates'
OL,17,FCourt on Friday and will next appear
OL,18,Fat Woolwich Crown Court on May 22.
OL,20,FBoth men were remanded into custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
