OL,3,CTwo men and three teenagers charged
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged rape of girl
OL,6,FTwo of the boys were remanded into
OL,7,Fyouth detention, and the third was
OL,8,Freleased into the care of the local
OL,9,Fauthority, Kent Police said.
